<p>1060 bis. In a letter dated 5 November 2009, the Government of Indonesia responded 
to the communication sent on 4 September 2009 as follows. On 21 August 2009, in 
Abepura, Jayapura District, the District Police conducted a criminal investigation based on 
</p>
<p> United Nations A/HRC/13/22/Add.1/Corr.1
